* Tateiwa Shrine - enshrined deity is {{ill|lt=Amatsumara|Q10940368|WD=Q10940368|1=Ama-Tsu-Mara}}. A giant rock serves as the {{ill|lt=shintai|Q327532|WD=Q327532|1=Shintai}}, and the shrine building is a small hokora. A festival is held on October 17.

